edu.xtec.jclic.edit

Class Editor

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
      • edu.xtec.jclic.edit.Editor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, MutableTreeNode, TreeNode
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ActivityBagEditor, ActivityBagElementEditor, ActivityEditor, ActivitySequenceEditor, ActivitySequenceElementEditor, AutoContentProviderEditor, JClicProjectEditor, MediaBagEditor, MediaBagElementEditor, MenuEditor, MenuElementEditor, ProjectLibraryEditor, ProjectSettingsEditor

    public abstract class Editor
extends DefaultMutableTreeNode
    This generic class allows to modify the content and properties of an associated Editable object. Editors provide methods to register listeners that will be informed about changes occurred in its associated data object. The class extends DefaultMutableTreeNode in order to make easy to implement a tree of dependences between editor classes.
    Version:
    13.09.10
    Author:
    Francesc Busquets (fbusquets@xtec.cat)
